# Claude / Google Drive handoff (Alan)

## Outbox (Cursor → Claude)

When Alan says **export for Claude**, **export to google**, **share with Claude**, **put on Google Drive**, or similar — save deliverables here by default:

`C:\Users\alan\Google Drive\Claude shared resources\Cursor Outputs for Claude\`

- Read and write freely (Google Drive Desktop sync).
- Use clear filenames; add `*-LATEST` for recurring artifacts when useful.
- Answers to Claude questions: `RESPONSE-<id>-LATEST.md` in the outbox.

## Inbox (Claude → Cursor)

`C:\Users\alan\Google Drive\Claude shared resources\Claude Questions for Cursor\`

When Alan says **check claude**, **process Claude inbox**, **check Claude questions**, **answer Claude handoff**, or similar:

1. Read `HANDOFF-RESPONSE-INDEX-LATEST.md` (canonical) or `CURSOR-HANDOFF-STATUS-LATEST.md`
2. Process each `QUESTION-*.md` with YAML `status: pending` (see inbox `README.md`)
3. Write `RESPONSE-<id>-LATEST.md` to outbox; move question to `processed\`
4. **Always** run `node scripts/claude-cursor-handoff/update-handoff-manifest.mjs` after processing (refreshes status + index for Claude)
5. **BUILD** questions: commit + push via **GitKraken MCP** (`git_add_or_commit`, `git_push`) — not Shell git (see `gitkraken-git-ops.mdc`)

Full agent prompt: `Chat AI Bot/scripts/claude-cursor-handoff/CURSOR-PROCESS-INBOX-PROMPT.md`

Hands-off cycle (every 15 min): Task `ClaudeCursorHandoff15Min` → `Run-HandoffCycle.ps1`

Claude instructions: `Claude shared resources/CLAUDE-HANDOFF-INSTRUCTIONS-LATEST.md`

## Rules

- Do not put secrets (.env, API keys, credentials) in Drive handoff folders.
- Repo source of truth stays in git/Dropbox; Drive is **handoff copies** only.

## Exception

AI GEO Audit `npm run export:claude` dashboard HTML may still target the parent folder (`Claude shared resources\LIVE-DASHBOARD-SNAPSHOT-revenue-truth-LATEST.html`) unless the user asks to change that script.
